## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-137">如果调用， <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> 并且没有任何要向后定位到的文档，则不 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 会执行导航，并引发异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-137">If you call <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> and there are not any documents to navigate back to, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> does not perform a navigation and an exception is thrown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-138">如果需要，可以检查属性的值， <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A> 以确定是否存在要向后定位到的文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-138">If you need to, you can inspect the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A> property to determine whether there are documents to navigate back to.</span></span>  
  
   
  
