## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-156"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> 在实现它的文档加载完成之前，不应调用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-156"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-157">可以通过处理事件来检测文档的加载完成时间 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-157">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-158">下面的示例演示如何使用从应用程序调用文档中的脚本函数 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-158">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-159">在此示例中，脚本函数没有参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-159">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-160">下面是 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 实现将从调用的脚本函数的文档 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-160">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-161">下面演示了 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] 用于调用文档中的脚本函数的实现 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-161">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-169"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> 在实现它的文档加载完成之前，不应调用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-169"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-170">可以通过处理事件来检测文档的加载完成时间 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-170">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-171">如果未将足够的参数值传递给要调用的脚本，则未将值传递给的参数将具有未定义的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-171">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-172">如果传递的参数值过多，将忽略多余的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-172">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-173">下面的示例演示如何使用从应用程序调用文档中的脚本函数 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-173">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-174">在此示例中，脚本函数需要参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-174">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-175">下面是实现将从调用的脚本函数的文档 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-175">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-176">下面演示了 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] 用于调用文档中的脚本函数的实现 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-176">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-190">调用与 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> 设置属性的效果相同 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-190">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-191"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 需要以声明方式指定 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 初始化时导航到的初始文档的开发人员使用标记 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-191"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-192">使用 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> 方法导航到可能包含转义符的 URL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-192">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-193">使用 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> 方法导航到 <xref:System.Uri> 不包含转义符的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-193">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-194">下面的示例演示如何使用 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 通过方法导航到文档 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-194">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-212">使用 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> 方法导航到可能包含转义符的 URL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-212">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-213">使用 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> 方法导航到 <xref:System.Uri> 不包含转义符的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-213">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-214">下面的示例演示如何通过指定 "about：空白" 目标导航到文档并在新的浏览器窗口中打开它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-214">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-225">如果 `stream` 参数为 `null` ，则 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 导航到空白文档 ( "关于：空白" ) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-225">If the `stream` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-226">如果流参数的 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 格式无效，则它将显示为纯文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-226">If the stream parameter is not in a valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-227">导航后， <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 将为 `null` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-227">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-228">下面的示例演示如何导航到包含文档的流。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-228">The following example shows how to navigate to a stream that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStreamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a stream  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream source = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  
  // Navigate to HTML document stream  
  this.webBrowser.NavigateToStream(source);  
}  
```

  
  
