 <span data-ttu-id="0aab4-234">如果 text 参数的 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 格式无效，则它将显示为纯文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0aab4-234">If the text parameter is not in valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
